#: home/templates/home/pricing.html:1065
msgid ""
"ExactusPay believes in pricing that is as clear and transparent as our "
"payroll reporting. We understand that every business has a unique footprint, "
"which is why our pricing model is tailored to the specific countries and "
"regions where you operate."
msgstr ""
